---
title: Grilled BBQ-Chipotle Pork Chops with Sweet Potato Wedges and Charred Corn Salad
description: Sweet and smoky BBQ-chipotle sauce coats these grilled pork chops for some Southwest-style flare! Corn charred on the grill is a quintessential must-have for the season and makes this delicious summer plate sing. Sweet potato wedges roast in the oven while you enjoy the outdoors. Let the grilling begin!
